message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION_FV_TP_NAME_EXISTS
message.locale: A typical picture with this Name already exists for this questionnaire version.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION_FV_TP_FOR_RELEASED_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: This questionnaire version has been released and a typical picture cannot be created. To create a typical picture you must first create a new In Edit version of the questionnaire.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION_FV_TP_FOR_RELEASED_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION
message.locale: This version has been released and cannot be modified. To modify the typical picture you must first create a new In Edit version.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREDECSIONOUTCOME_FV_TP_FOR_RELEASED_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION
message.locale: This typical picture has been released and a new decision outcome cannot be added. To add a new decision outcome you must create a new In Edit version of the typical picture.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREDECSIONOUTCOME_FV_TP_FOR_ALLREADY_DECISION_OUTCOME_COMBINATION_EXITS
message.locale: This combination of Decision Matrix and Outcome already exists for this typical picture version.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION_FV_TP_FOR_NEWVERSION_INEDIT_ALLREADY_EXISTS
message.locale: There is currently an in edit version of this typical picture. The in edit version must be released or deleted before a new version can be created.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION_FV_TP_FOR_NEWVERSION_RELEASED_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: A new version of a typical picture cannot be created as the questionnaire is not In Edit.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREVERSION_FV_TP_FOR_NEWVERSION_REL_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: The questionnaire associated with this typical picture has been released. The Questionnaire must be in edit to release the typical picture.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREDECISIONOUTCOME_FV_TP_FOR_RELEASED_TYPICALPICTURE
message.locale: This typical picture has been released and cannot be modified. To remove the decision outcome a new In Edit version of the typical picture must be created.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTUREDECISIONOUTCOME_FV_TP_FOR_MODIFY_RELEASED_OUTCOME
message.locale: This typical picture has been released and cannot be modified. To modify a decision outcome you must create a new In Edit version of the typical picture.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTURE_FV_TP_FOR_ALREADY_RELEASED
message.locale: This typical picture has already been released.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTURE_FV_TP_FOR_DELETE_ALREADY_RELEASED
message.locale: This typical picture is not In Edit and therefore cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_TYPICALPICTURE_FV_TP_FOR_OUTCOME_DELETE_ALREADY_RELEASED
message.locale: This typical picture has been released and cannot be modified. To remove the decision outcome a new In Edit version of the typical picture must be created.
